1. *Podne* je došao, a s njim i hladan vetar. (Noon has come, and with it a cold wind.)
2. Naš dom se nalazi udaljen od grada samo nekoliko minuta *podne*vog hoda. (Our home is located just a few minutes away by foot.)
3. Ona je uvek bila tu u *podne*, kako bi održala svoje obaveze. (She was always there at noon to fulfill her obligations.)
4. *Podne*vom suncu, naši su planovi postali jasni. (With the midday sun, our plans became clear.)
5. *Podne* je vreme za odmor i predah. (Noon is a time for rest and respite.)